<FONT COLOR=#0000FF> <B>Sabishi</B> さん </FONT><FONT SIZE=2>  　 <FONT SIZE=2>2002/04/19 (金) 12:38</FONT></FONT><P><font size=2><P>Sorry for lots of english in this post..<BR><BR>I think many know about LoS (Legacy of Steel) and Tigole..  He is going to work for Blizzard and become game designer for World of Warcraft and design quests for it.  I think many strong guilds of all servers are getting very tired by EQ.  Many high end fights are just so badly designed.  Not fun and sometimes so bugged.  Items designs are also bad.  With AC cap, who needs more AC, with primal, who needs STR, DEX, AGI?  STA is still good, but I am sure most melee will get 255 STA.  Savings are sometimes so useless against Dragon resist AE.  Not sure about others, but I think SoL is a very poor expansion for EQ.  The new grahpics are bad, the new quests are really boring and need too much time camping keys...  Bane weapons need so many rare items and so many people to camp...  So many mobs are bugged and impossible to kill (emperor, Vxxx the cursed, Vulak ring, AoF ring,..) VI must wake up and improve EQ, fix SoL and make it fun and interesting before trying to earn more money from us by making another expansion....<BR><BR></P></font>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1}>
